Interface ContactInfo

All Known Implementing Classes:
PendingContact
public interface ContactInfo

Interface to query details for a contact of two collision geometries.

getDefaultFrictionDirections

void getDefaultFrictionDirections(com.jme.math.Vector3f primaryStore,
                                  com.jme.math.Vector3f secondaryStore)
Query the default for the directions of the friction. Both directions are perpendicular to each other and perpendicular to the contact normal.

Parameters:
primaryStore - store for first friction direction as specified in ContactHandlingDetails.getFrictionDirection(com.jme.math.Vector3f) (cannot be null)
secondaryStore - second direction store (may be null)
